---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
import { SITE } from '../data/site';

const schema = JSON.stringify({
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "Article",
  "headline": "The HappyBein Manifesto",
  "description": "Our North Star: simplify the complexity of our world so every citizen and leader can make conscious, informed, and impactful decisions.",
  "url": `${SITE.url}/manifesto`,
  "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "HappyBein", "logo": { "@type": "ImageObject", "url": `${SITE.url}/images/logo.png` }},
  "datePublished": "2021-01-01",
  "dateModified": "2026-05-13"
});
---

<Base
  title="The HappyBein Manifesto – Clarity for a Complex World"
  description="Our North Star: simplify the complexity of our world so every citizen and leader can make conscious, informed, and impactful decisions."
  canonical="https://happybein.com/manifesto"
  ogType="article"
  schema={schema}
>
  <div class="page-hero">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
      <div class="section-label">Our Foundation</div>
      <h1 class="font-display font-black text-ink tracking-tight leading-[1.1] mb-4 max-w-2xl"
          style="font-size:clamp(1.8rem,3.5vw,2.9rem);">The HappyBein Manifesto</h1>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed max-w-xl">Clarity for a Complex World — why we exist, how we operate, and what we believe.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <section class="py-16 px-5">
    <div class="max-w-[760px] mx-auto prose-hb">

      <h2>🌟 Our North Star</h2>
      <div class="north-star">
        <p>To simplify the complexity of our world so that every citizen and leader can make conscious, informed, and impactful decisions.</p>
      </div>
      <p>We believe that individual well-being and collective progress are not accidental. They are the result of conscious choices. But in a world drowning in noise, making good choices has never been harder.</p>

      <hr />

      <h2>1. How We Operate: The Architect and The Instrument</h2>
      <p>To bridge the gap between abstract wisdom and daily action, we operate through two distinct vehicles:</p>

      <h3>HappyBein (The Foundation)</h3>
      <p><em>The Architect & The Source.</em> HappyBein is the non-profit organisation dedicated to the mission of holistic well-being. We act as the <strong>Research Studio</strong> — studying societal challenges, curating best practices, and defining the vision. We answer the question: <em>"Why does this matter?"</em></p>

      <h3>YeahVibe (The Platform)</h3>
      <p><em>The Instrument & The Solution.</em> YeahVibe is the <strong>Digital Tool</strong> built by HappyBein. It is the decision-support ecosystem where our research comes to life — the practical interface users interact with daily. We answer the question: <em>"How do I apply this today?"</em></p>

      <hr />

      <h2>2. The Content: What YeahVibe Delivers</h2>

      <h3>Stream A: Internal Efficiency</h3>
      <p><em>The Engine.</em> Via YeahVibe, we provide:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Process Optimisation:</strong> Checklists and frameworks to save time.</li>
        <li><strong>Personal Organisation:</strong> Tools to clear mental clutter and prioritise goals.</li>
        <li><em>Goal: To move the individual from Overwhelmed to Empowered.</em></li>
      </ul>

      <h3>Stream B: External Understanding</h3>
      <p><em>The Map.</em> Via YeahVibe, we provide:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Societal Simplification:</strong> Decoding complex global issues into plain language.</li>
        <li><strong>Systemic Insight:</strong> Showing how the state of the world impacts daily life.</li>
        <li><em>Goal: To move the citizen from Confused to Informed.</em></li>
      </ul>

      <hr />

      <h2>3. The Synthesis</h2>
      <div class="synthesis-box">
        <p>We believe that <strong>Internal Stability</strong> (Stream A) + <strong>External Clarity</strong> (Stream B) = <strong>Impactful Decisions</strong>.</p>
        <p class="mt-3"><strong>HappyBein</strong> exists to foster this balance. <strong>YeahVibe</strong> exists to deliver it.</p>
      </div>

      <p class="text-center font-display font-extrabold text-ink text-[1.2rem] mt-10">Simplify. Understand. Decide.</p>

    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-16 px-5 text-center" style="background:#E8F7F7;">
    <div class="teal-gradient rounded-2xl p-16 max-w-2xl mx-auto text-white" style="box-shadow:0 12px 40px rgba(42,191,191,0.2);">
      <h2 class="font-display font-extrabold leading-tight mb-4" style="font-size:clamp(1.4rem,2.5vw,2.1rem);">Start with YeahVibe</h2>
      <p class="opacity-90 mb-8">A structured approach to define meaningful goals — learn the essence of your well-being.</p>
      <a href="https://www.yeahvibe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn-white">Open YeahVibe →</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .prose-hb h2 { font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif; font-size:1.45rem; font-weight:800; color:#1A3333; margin:2.8rem 0 0.8rem; }
  .prose-hb h3 { font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif; font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:700; color:#1A9A9A; margin:1.6rem 0 0.5rem; }
  .prose-hb p  { margin-bottom:1.1rem; color:#2C4A4A; line-height:1.85; }
  .prose-hb ul { margin:0.5rem 0 1rem 1.5rem; list-style:disc; }
  .prose-hb ul li { margin-bottom:0.4rem; color:#2C4A4A; }
  .prose-hb hr { border:none; border-top:1px solid rgba(42,191,191,0.18); margin:2.5rem 0; }
  .north-star { background:#E8F7F7; border-left:4px solid #2ABFBF; padding:1.3rem 1.6rem; border-radius:0 8px 8px 0; margin:1.5rem 0; }
  .north-star p { font-family:'Nunito',sans-serif; font-style:italic; font-weight:700; color:#1A3333; margin:0; }
  .synthesis-box { background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1A9A9A,#2ABFBF); color:white; padding:2rem; border-radius:8px; margin:2rem 0; }
  .synthesis-box p { color:white; margin:0; }
</style>
